text: Koyilandy railway station (Code: QLD) is a railway station in Kozhikode District, Kerala and falls under the Palakkad railway division of the Southern Railway Zone, Indian Railways. == Gallery == File:Koyilandy RS.jpg| ==References== Category:Railway stations in Kozhikode district Category:Palakkad railway division Category:Koyilandy area
